{
  "dashboard": {
    "id": null,
    "title": "EasyLife AI - Cost Monitoring",
    "tags": ["easylife-ai", "cost", "monitoring"],
    "style": "dark",
    "timezone": "browser",
    "panels": [
      {
        "id": 1,
        "title": "Resource Usage by Service",
        "type": "stat",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(rate(container_cpu_usage_seconds_total[5m])) by (pod)",
            "legendFormat": "{{ pod }}"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "short",
            "color": {
              "mode": "thresholds"
            },
            "thresholds": {
              "steps": [
                {"color": "green", "value": 0},
                {"color": "yellow", "value": 0.5},
                {"color": "red", "value": 1}
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 0}
      },
      {
        "id": 2,
        "title": "Memory Usage by Service",
        "type": "graph",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(container_memory_usage_bytes) by (pod)",
            "legendFormat": "{{ pod }}"
          }
        ],
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 0}
      },
      {
        "id": 3,
        "title": "Pod Count by Service",
        "type": "stat",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "count(kube_pod_info) by (app)",
            "legendFormat": "{{ app }}"
          }
        ],
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 8}
      },
      {
        "id": 4,
        "title": "Request Rate vs Cost",
        "type": "graph",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "rate(http_requests_total[5m])",
            "legendFormat": "{{ job }} - Requests/sec"
          },
          {
            "expr": "sum(rate(container_cpu_usage_seconds_total[5m])) by (job)",
            "legendFormat": "{{ job }} - CPU Usage"
          }
        ],
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 16}
      },
      {
        "id": 5,
        "title": "Cost Optimization Recommendations",
        "type": "text",
        "options": {
          "content": "# Cost Optimization Recommendations\n\n## Current Status\n- **CPU Usage**: Monitor for over-provisioning\n- **Memory Usage**: Check for memory leaks\n- **Pod Count**: Optimize replica counts\n\n## Recommendations\n1. **Right-size Resources**: Adjust CPU/memory limits based on actual usage\n2. **Horizontal Pod Autoscaling**: Enable HPA for dynamic scaling\n3. **Resource Quotas**: Set appropriate resource quotas\n4. **Pod Disruption Budgets**: Ensure high availability\n5. **Cost Monitoring**: Track resource costs over time\n\n## Alerts\n- High CPU usage (>80% for 5 minutes)\n- High memory usage (>90% for 5 minutes)\n- Pod count exceeding limits\n- Resource quota violations"
        },
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 24}
      }
    ],
    "time": {
      "from": "now-1h",
      "to": "now"
    },
    "refresh": "30s"
  }
}
